{"type": "root", "attrs": {"icon": "DOP/rbdfracturedobject", "tags": "rigidbodies"}, "body": [{"level": 0, "type": "title", "indent": 0, "text": ["RBD Fractured Object"], "extent": [50, 75]}, {"type": "summary", "indent": 0, "text": ["Creates a number of RBD Objects from SOP Geometry. These individual RBD Objects are created from the geometry primitive groups."], "extent": [75, 211]}, {"level": 2, "id": null, "container": true, "type": "h", "indent": 0, "text": ["Overview"], "extent": [211, 226], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 0, "text": ["The RBD Fractured Object creates multiple ", {"scheme": "Icon", "value": "DOP/rbdobject", "type": "link", "text": "", "fullpath": "/shelf/DOP/rbdobject"}, {"scheme": null, "value": "/shelf/rbdobject", "type": "link", "text": ["RBD objects"], "fullpath": "/shelf/rbdobject"}, " inside the ", {"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/obj/dopnet", "type": "link", "text": ["dynamic operation simulation"], "fullpath": "/nodes/obj/dopnet"}, ". It takes the geometry from the given surface operator path and breaks it into pieces according to the ", {"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/dop/group", "type": "link", "text": ["group mask"], "fullpath": "/nodes/dop/group"}, ". This tool is useful to simulate an object shattering."], "extent": [226, 565]}, {"type": "note_group", "body": [{"type": "note", "indent": 0, "role": "item", "extent": [565, 571], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 8, "text": ["This tool is meant to be used with user-defined fractures. It will not break up the surface for you. It will create RBD objects out of the pieces you give it."], "extent": [571, 739]}], "container": true}], "container": true, "role": "item_group"}]}, {"level": 2, "id": "includeme", "container": true, "type": "h", "indent": 0, "text": ["Using RBD Fractured Objects"], "extent": [739, 785], "body": [{"type": "ord_group", "body": [{"blevel": 6, "type": "ord", "indent": 4, "text": ["Select the geometry to convert to an RBD fractured object."], "extent": [785, 860]}, {"blevel": 6, "type": "ord", "indent": 4, "text": ["Define the pieces to be fractured. For example, using the ", {"scheme": null, "value": "/shelf/shatter", "type": "link", "text": ["Shatter tool"], "fullpath": "/shelf/shatter"}, "."], "extent": [860, 956]}, {"blevel": 6, "type": "ord", "indent": 4, "text": ["Select the object and click the ", {"scheme": "Icon", "value": "DOP/rbdfracturedobject", "type": "link", "text": "", "fullpath": "/shelf/DOP/rbdfracturedobject"}, {"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/dop/rbdfracturedobject", "type": "link", "text": ["RBD Fractured Object"], "fullpath": "/nodes/dop/rbdfracturedobject"}, " tool on the ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Rigid Bodies"]}, " tab."], "extent": [956, 1113]}, {"blevel": 6, "type": "ord", "indent": 4, "text": ["Choose whether to use an ", {"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/dop/rbdpackedobject", "type": "link", "text": ["RBD Packed Object"], "fullpath": "/nodes/dop/rbdpackedobject"}, " or an ", {"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/dop/rbdfracturedobject", "type": "link", "text": ["RBD Fractured Object"], "fullpath": "/nodes/dop/rbdfracturedobject"}, "."], "extent": [1113, 1252], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 0, "text": ["RBD Packed Objects are useful for large simulations since they are much faster, use less memory, and are smaller to write to disk. They can also be influenced by ", {"scheme": null, "value": "/dopparticles/forces", "type": "link", "text": ["POP Forces"], "fullpath": "/dopparticles/forces"}, ", such as drag. Packed Objects can not interact with other solvers such as cloth and fluids. They also only work with ", {"scheme": null, "value": "/destruction/constraints", "type": "link", "text": ["Constraint Networks"], "fullpath": "/destruction/constraints"}, "."], "extent": [16, 377]}], "container": true}], "container": true}, {"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": [{"scheme": "Image", "value": "/images/shelf/rbd_fracture_object_before.jpg", "type": "img", "text": ""}, "  ", {"scheme": "Image", "value": "/images/shelf/rbd_fracture_object_after.jpg", "type": "img", "text": ""}], "extent": [1294, 1409]}, {"type": "note_group", "body": [{"type": "note", "indent": 4, "role": "item", "extent": [1409, 1419], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 8, "text": ["Once you convert geometry to an RBD fractured object you can only ", {"scheme": null, "value": "/basics/handles", "type": "link", "text": ["transform, rotate, and scale"], "fullpath": "/basics/handles"}, " it when it is on the first frame."], "extent": [1419, 1575]}], "container": true}], "container": true, "role": "item_group"}]}, {"type": "para", "indent": 0, "text": ["For specific parameter help see the ", {"scheme": "Icon", "value": "DOP/rbdpackedobject", "type": "link", "text": "", "fullpath": "/shelf/DOP/rbdpackedobject"}, {"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/dop/rbdpackedobject", "type": "link", "text": ["RBD Packed Object"], "fullpath": "/nodes/dop/rbdpackedobject"}, " or ", {"scheme": "Icon", "value": "DOP/rbdfracturedobject", "type": "link", "text": "", "fullpath": "/shelf/DOP/rbdfracturedobject"}, {"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/dop/rbdfracturedobject", "type": "link", "text": ["RBD Fractured Object"], "fullpath": "/nodes/dop/rbdfracturedobject"}, " help."], "extent": [1575, 1772]}, {"level": 2, "id": null, "container": true, "type": "h", "indent": 0, "text": ["Switching to the dynamics level"], "extent": [1772, 1810], "body": [{"type": "ord_group", "body": [{"blevel": 2, "type": "ord", "indent": 0, "text": ["Click the ", {"scheme": "Icon", "value": "TOOLS/select_dynamics", "type": "link", "text": "", "fullpath": "/shelf/TOOLS/select_dynamics"}, "Dynamics Select Mode button on the ", {"scheme": null, "value": "/basics/select", "type": "link", "text": ["selector and handle controls toolbar"], "fullpath": "/basics/select"}, "."], "extent": [1810, 1942]}, {"blevel": 2, "type": "ord", "indent": 0, "text": ["Click ", {"keys": ["LMB"], "type": "keys", "text": null}, " the RBD fracture object in the ", {"scheme": null, "value": "/ref/views/3dview", "type": "link", "text": ["scene view"], "fullpath": "/ref/views/3dview"}, "."], "extent": [1942, 2022]}], "container": true}, {"type": "para", "indent": 0, "text": ["See ", {"scheme": null, "value": "/examples/nodes/dop/rbdfracturedobject/ShatterDebris", "type": "link", "text": ["this example file"], "fullpath": "/examples/nodes/dop/rbdfracturedobject/ShatterDebris"}, "."], "extent": [2022, 2101]}]}, {"level": 1, "id": "related", "container": true, "type": "related_section", "indent": 0, "role": "section", "extent": [2101, 2110], "body": [{"type": "bullet_group", "body": [{"blevel": 2, "type": "bullet", "indent": 0, "text": [{"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/dop/rbdobject", "type": "link", "text": ["RBD Object"], "fullpath": "/nodes/dop/rbdobject"}], "extent": [2110, 2145]}, {"blevel": 2, "type": "bullet", "indent": 0, "text": [{"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/dop/rbdglueobject", "type": "link", "text": ["RBD Glue Object"], "fullpath": "/nodes/dop/rbdglueobject"}], "extent": [2145, 2188]}, {"blevel": 2, "type": "bullet", "indent": 0, "text": [{"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/dop/rbdkeyactive", "type": "link", "text": ["RBD Keyframe Active"], "fullpath": "/nodes/dop/rbdkeyactive"}], "extent": [2188, 2234]}], "container": true}], "text": "Related"}], "title": ["RBD Fractured Object"], "summary": ["Creates a number of RBD Objects from SOP Geometry. These individual RBD Objects are created from the geometry primitive groups."], "included": ["/shelf/rbdpackedobject_choose"]}